CustomField.description: This field is optional and can be collected as part of a workflow. It is the percentage that is added to (or subtracted from) the index to determine the applicable rate for a given account tier with variable rate tiers.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The percentage that is added to (or subtracted from) the index to determine the applicable rate for a given account tier with variable rate tiers.
CustomField.label: Tiered Margin Percent
